playstore_details.title: SmartID OTP
playstore_details.description:
SmartID OTP app provides users with enhanced 2-Factor Authentication via OTP, thereby enables secure log-in for SAVIS' service subscribers. With additional layer of security, existing users will be required to input both a password and verification code generated by this app. This advance authentication app is a secure and convenient solution for commercial use.

- Unlock app via PIN code/TouchID/FaceID for the ultimate convenience
- Start using 2-Factor Authentication by scanning QR code to link device with services
